: Michael Cohen to Deliver Shocking Testimony About Trump</span><span class="related-author" data-reactid="412"><span data-reactid="413">BY </span><span class="related-author-name" data-reactid="414">EMILY JANE FOX</span></span></div></a><div id="PolarAdArticleRiser88x32_frame_wrapper" class="display-polar-ad related-content-item" data-reactid="415"><a class="related-content-item" data-source="parsely-related" href="/news/2019/02/donald-trump-robert-mueller-special-counsel-report" data-reactid="416"><div class="related-image-wrapper" data-reactid="417"><div data-reactid="418"><div class="component-lazy pending" data-component="Lazy" data-reactid="419"></div></div></div><div class="related-text-wrapper" data-reactid="420"><span class="related-hed" data-reactid="421">Robert Mueller Appears After Something Really, Really Big</span><span class="related-author" data-reactid="422"><span data-reactid="423">BY </span><span class="related-author-name" data-reactid="424">ABIGAIL TRACY</span></span></div></a></div></div><div class="riser-footer" data-reactid="425"><span class="riser-toggle" data-reactid="426">SEEK</span></div></div><!-- react-empty: 427 --><!-- react-empty: 428 --></div><footer class="component-site-footer" data-reactid="429"><div class="footer-wrapper" data-reactid="430"><div class="connect-container" data-reactid="431"><div class="subscribe-container" data-reactid="432"><div class="component component-newsletter-subscribe footer" data-reactid="433"><div class="wrapper" data-reactid="434"><div class="main-subscribe-container " data-reactid="435"><div class="logo" data-reactid="436"></div><div class="hed  subscribe" data-reactid="437">NEWSLETTER SIGN UP</div><div class="" id="newsletter-footer" data-reactid="438"><form action="https://user-service.condenastdigital.com/open/newsletter/entries" method="POST" class="subscribe" data-reactid="439"><input type="email" class="form-input" value="" data-reactid="440"/><button type="submit" class="btn-newletter-subscrib