“four or five minutes each.” (Imagine having a trip you make to the pool with your kids covered in this sort of breathless detail.)</p>\n<p>There is still much more. George and Charlotte were “impeccably behaved” at the pool. George won the races, “swimming front like a dog-paddle style, and jumping in from a squatting position [on] the side.” Charlotte was doing “sitting dives,” and she apparently repeatedly said, ‘Look, mummy&#8212;I’m diving in.’” (A nod to “Shallow,” perhaps?) This onlooker stated, “Both the children swam unaided and were super confident.” Kate, meanwhile, “looked stunning”: she had “her hair up in a butterfly type hair clip and looked extremely elegant.”</p>\n<p>Per the outlet, both George and Charlotte have returned to school Monday in London.</p>","rubric":"Royals","socialTitle":"Kate Middleton Took Her Kids on a Luxury Spa Visit","socialDescription":"Prince George and Princess Charlotte went for a swim the day before Meghan Markle was showered in New York.","seoTitle":"Kate Middleton Took Her Kids on a Luxury Spa Visit","seoDescription":"Prince George and Princess Charlotte went for a swim the day before Meghan Markle was showered in New York.","channel":"Style","subChannel":"Royals","issueDate":"","ledeCaption":"","contentSource":"web","canonicalUrl":"","interactiveOverride":"","contentType":"","textMimeType":"","tags":["kate middleton"],"revisionAuthor":"Josh Duboff","meta":{"collectionName":"articles","modelName":"article","publishable":true,"identifiable":true,"image":false,"archived":false,"hallable":true,"hierarchical":false},"id":"5c7418c654544e5e8adca9f5","revision":5,"createdAt":"February 25, 2019 11:33 am","modifiedAt":"February 25, 2019 11:39 am","revisionCreatedAt":"February 25, 2019 11:39 am","_embedded":{"categories-channels":[{"fields":{"name":"Style","slug":"style","revisionAuthor":"aviator-scripts-categories-migration","meta":{"collectionName":"categories","modelName":"category","publishable":false,"identifiable":false,"imag