o named Herbie, the school dog. <em>People</em> <a href=\"https://people.com/royals/kate-middleton-meets-herbie-school-dog/\">offers</a> an amusingly detailed breakdown of what went down when the duchess and the dog met: “She knelt down to give him a pat, only for the pooch to put his paws on her arms to get a closer sniff. But Kate didn’t seem to mind, smiling and chatting with his student handler as Herbie poked his nose around her signature bouncy blowout.”</p>\n<p>There is (brief) video footage of this Kate-Herbie meeting, do not fret:</p>\n<div class=\"embed block row social-twitter\"><blockquote class=\"embed twitter-embed-component twitter-tweet twitter-tweet\" lang=\"en\" data-type=\"twitter\" data-url=\"https://twitter.com/RE_DailyMail/status/1092780144786395136\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/RE_DailyMail/status/1092780144786395136\">https://twitter.com/RE_DailyMail/status/1092780144786395136</a></p></blockquote></div>","rubric":"Royals","socialTitle":"Kate Middleton Shares an Item That Sparks Joy for Her","socialDescription":"The Duchess of Cambridge also reveals a recent meal she prepared with George and Charlotte.\n","seoTitle":"Kate Middleton Shares an Item That Sparks Joy for Her","seoDescription":"The Duchess of Cambridge also reveals a recent meal she prepared with George and Charlotte.\n","channel":"Style","subChannel":"Royals","issueDate":"","ledeCaption":"","contentSource":"web","canonicalUrl":"","interactiveOverride":"","contentType":"","textMimeType":"","tags":["kate middleton"],"revisionAuthor":"Josh Duboff","meta":{"collectionName":"articles","modelName":"article","publishable":true,"identifiable":true,"image":false,"archived":false,"hallable":true,"hierarchical":false},"id":"5c59ace2ba532c6650dee1bf","revision":7,"createdAt":"February 5, 2019 10:33 am","modifiedAt":"February 5, 2019 10:37 am","revisionCreatedAt":"February 5, 2019 10:37 am","_embedded":{"categories-channels":[{"fields":{"name":"Style","slug":"style","revisionAuthor":"aviat