healthy-yoga-meditation?inline\">mellowing of Prince Harry</a></p>\n<p>&#8212; Here’s our critic’s <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2019/01/the-souvenir-movie-review-tilda-swinton-joanna-hogg?inline\">favorite film out of Sundance</a></p>\n<p>&#8212; How Brandi Carlile became the <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/style/2019/01/grammy-nominated-brandi-carlile-on-female-headlining-music-festival?inline\">2019 Grammys’ most-nominated woman</a></p>\n<p>&#8212; A visual depiction of <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/style/photos/2019/01/donald-trump-melania-anniversary-slideshow?inline\">Donald and Melania’s unique commitment to one another</a></p>\n<p>Looking for more? <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/newsletters\">Sign up</a> for our daily newsletter and never miss a story.</p>","rubric":"super bowl liii","socialTitle":"Gisele Bündchen Celebrated at the Super Bowl Like She’d Never Seen the Patriots Win","socialDescription":"When Tom Brady and his team pulled off a victory Sunday night, Bündchen joined him on the field for a big kiss.","seoTitle":"Gisele Bündchen Celebrated at the Super Bowl Like She’d Never Seen the Patriots Win","seoDescription":"When Tom Brady and his team pulled off a victory Sunday night, Bündchen joined him on the field for a big kiss.","channel":"Style","subChannel":"","issueDate":"","ledeCaption":"","contentSource":"web","canonicalUrl":"","interactiveOverride":"","contentType":"","textMimeType":"","tags":["gisele bundchen","tom brady"],"revisionAuthor":"Hilary Weaver","meta":{"collectionName":"articles","modelName":"article","publishable":true,"identifiable":true,"image":false,"archived":false,"hallable":true,"hierarchical":false},"id":"5c585be8ba532c6650dee185","revision":12,"createdAt":"February 4, 2019 10:36 am","modifiedAt":"February 4, 2019 10:48 am","revisionCreatedAt":"February 4, 2019 10:48 am","_embedded":{"categories-channels":[{"fields":{"name":"Style","slug":"style","revisionAuthor":"aviator-scripts-categories